<h1> Using BBA API </h1>
<small> POST = http requests, Post or post = model for hamburger </small>
<hr/>
<div class="row">
  <h3> Admin Console </h3>
  <code>/admin</code>: Access Admin Console
</div>

<div class="row">
  <div class="col s12">
    <h3> Post (hamburger) GET requests </h3>
    <code>/api/posts</code>: Access first page of posts (hamburgers)<br>
    <code>/api/posts?page=2</code>: Access page by params (hamburgers)<br>
    <code>/api/posts/:id</code>: Access post at ID (hamburgers)<br>
  </div>
  <div class="col s12">
    <h3> Post (hamburger) POST ðŸ˜–requests </h3>
    POST <code>/api/posts</code>: Add new post (hamburger place)<br>
    Acceptable Params:
    <p> { <br>
      post[title]: <span class="value">Name of Burger </span>,<br>
      post[description]: <span class="value"> Description of Burger</span>,<br>
      post[location]: <span class="value"> Retaurant name</span>,<br>
      post[pic]: <span class="value"> Pic URL</span>,<br>
      post[user_id]: <span class="value"> User ID </span>,<br>
    }</p>
  </div>
  <div class="col s12">
    <h3> Post (hamburger) PUT requests </h3>
    PUT<code>/api/posts/:id</code>: Edits post at given ID(hamburger place)<br>
    Acceptable Params:
    <p> { <br>
      post[title]: <span class="value">Name of Burger </span>,<br>
      post[description]: <span class="value"> Description of Burger</span>,<br>
      post[location]: <span class="value"> Retaurant name</span>,<br>
      post[pic]: <span class="value"> Pic URL</span>,<br>
      post[user_id]: <span class="value"> User ID </span>,<br>
    }</p>
  </div>
  <div class="col s12">
    <h3> Post (hamburger) DELETE requests </h3>
    DELETE<code>/api/posts/:id</code>: Deletes post at given ID(hamburger place)<br>
  </div>
</div>
<hr/>
<div class="row">
  <h3> Vote (hamburger) PUT requests </h3>
  PUT<code>/api/posts/:id/vote</code>: Add's vote to post at given ID(hamburger place)<br>
  Acceptable Params:
  <p> { <br>
    vote[user_id]: <span class="value">User ID </span>,<br>
  }</p>
</div>
